node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hannah Hillam on September 17, 2021. May be a cartoon of text.

node.text: Yoga Mat Purgatory (DAY 2 of FanX is over! Thanks for joining me on the livestream earlier! And to all those who came to my booth, THANK YOU. This has been one of the coolest experiences of my life. Also i reorganized my booth a little today since things kept falling down all day yesterday 😂)

node.text: I’m so tired and my voice is gone from talking for like 8 hours straight but I had so much fun today at #fanx2021. Thank you to those who came and said hi and bought some stickers and prints! It was surreal and exciting to meet you. I’ll be here tomorrow and Saturday at booth A1522 (in artist alley. They labeled the booths really badly and it’s confusing)
